Sand Skink plots

The structure of the skink data set shows there are three values 0, 1, 2, NA. Although the data looks quantitative, it is actually qualitative with: 0 representing - no traces found 1 representing - traces found 2 representing - sand skinks found NA representing - no observations made

So in this case finding the average, max, min is not useful. Hence we continued to find the count of 0’s, 1’s, 2’s for each year to get the number of sand skinks found/not found in each year.

Count of observations on sand skins made in each year

The below R script is used to get the counts in each year

Data Frame to plot time series data of Crooked Lake Sandhil

cls1 <- data.frame(Year=numeric(), NoTracks=numeric(), Tracks=numeric(), SkinkPresent=numeric(), NotObserved=numeric())
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2006, NoTracks=count06[1,2], Tracks=count06[2,2], SkinkPresent=count06[3,2], NotObserved=0 ))
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2011, NoTracks=count11[1,2], Tracks=count11[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=count11[3,2] ))
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2012, NoTracks=count12[1,2], Tracks=count12[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=0 ))
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2013, NoTracks=count13[1,2], Tracks=count13[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=0 ))
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2014, NoTracks=count14[1,2], Tracks=count14[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=0 ))
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2015, NoTracks=count15[1,2], Tracks=count15[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=0 ))
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2016, NoTracks=count16[1,2], Tracks=count16[2,2], SkinkPresent=count16[3,2], NotObserved=0 ))
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2017, NoTracks=count17[1,2], Tracks=count17[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=count17[3,2] ))
cls1 <- rbind(cls1, data.frame(Year=2018, NoTracks=count18[1,2], Tracks=count18[2,2], SkinkPresent=count18[3,2], NotObserved=0 ))

Crooked Lake Sandhil plots

library(ggplot2)

p1 <- ggplot() + 
  geom_line(aes(y = NoTracks, x = Year, color="No tracks present"), data = cls1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = Tracks, x = Year, color="Tracks found"), data = cls1)+
  geom_line(aes(y = SkinkPresent, x = Year, color="Skink found"), data = cls1)+
  geom_line(aes(y = NotObserved, x = Year, color="Not observed"), data = cls1)+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks=seq(2006,2018,2)) + 
  theme(text=element_text(family="Tahoma"))

p1 + labs(title = "Crooked Lake Sandhil Sand Skink observations", x = "Year", y = "Count")

Hickory Lake Scrub plots

hls1 <- data.frame(Year=numeric(), NoTracks=numeric(), Tracks=numeric(), SkinkPresent=numeric(), NotObserved=numeric())
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2006, NoTracks=count06[1,2], Tracks=count06[2,2], SkinkPresent=count06[3,2], NotObserved=count06[4,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2009, NoTracks=count09[1,2], Tracks=count09[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=count09[3,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2010, NoTracks=count10[1,2], Tracks=count10[2,2], SkinkPresent=count10[3,2], NotObserved=count10[4,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2011, NoTracks=count11[1,2], Tracks=count11[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=count11[3,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2012, NoTracks=count12[1,2], Tracks=count12[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=count12[3,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2013, NoTracks=count13[1,2], Tracks=count13[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=count13[3,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2014, NoTracks=count14[1,2], Tracks=count14[2,2], SkinkPresent=count14[3,2], NotObserved=count14[4,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2015, NoTracks=count15[1,2], Tracks=count15[2,2], SkinkPresent=count15[3,2], NotObserved=0 ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2016, NoTracks=count16[1,2], Tracks=count16[2,2], SkinkPresent=count16[3,2], NotObserved=count16[4,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2017, NoTracks=count17[1,2], Tracks=count17[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=count17[3,2] ))
hls1 <- rbind(hls1, data.frame(Year=2018, NoTracks=count18[1,2], Tracks=count18[2,2], SkinkPresent=0, NotObserved=0 ))

library(ggplot2)

h1 <- ggplot() + 
  geom_line(aes(y = NoTracks, x = Year, color="No tracks present"), data = hls1) +
  geom_line(aes(y = Tracks, x = Year, color="Tracks found"), data = hls1)+
  geom_line(aes(y = SkinkPresent, x = Year, color="Skink found"), data = hls1)+
  geom_line(aes(y = NotObserved, x = Year, color="Not observed"), data = hls1)+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks=seq(2006,2018,2)) + 
  theme(text=element_text(family="Tahoma"))

h1 + labs(title = "Hickory Lake Scrub Sand Skink Observations", x = "Year", y = "Count")
